text: Ahn Seung-In is a South Korean former professional footballer and current manager of Chungju Hummel. He made his debut on 1999, playing for Bucheon SK. He appeared in 117 games in his whole career, scored 7 goals and made 8 assists. == References == == External links == * Category:1973 births Category:Living people Category:South Korean footballers Category:South Korean football managers Category:Jeju United FC players Category:K League 1 players Category:Chungju Hummel FC managers Category:Association football midfielders
